Why is George Soros making Brexit supporters angry?

2016-06-22

As well as David Beckham, billionaire investor George Soros came out for Remain on Tuesday, warning that leaving the EU would be dangerous for jobs and for the pound.

“Our total position by Black Wednesday had to be worth almost $10 billion. We planned to sell more than that. In fact, when [Chancellor] Norman Lamont said just before the devaluation that he would borrow nearly $15 billion to defend sterling, we were amused because that was about how much we wanted to sell.”

